1
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,200
Young Master.

2
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,120
Father,

3
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,360
I

4
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,220
have returned.

5
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,039
You wretch.

6
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,720
The Xie family's

7
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,920
century-old reputation

8
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:29,680
is ruined overnight.

9
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:44,920
Xiao Jingyan.

10
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,520
We cannot exist under the same sky.

11
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:56,479
Boss.

12
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,160
What is it?

13
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:02,080
These are the newly made osmanthus pastries from the kitchen.

14
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:05,410
The steward specially ordered them to be sent for you to try.

15
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,000
They must have added double the osmanthus

16
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,260
to have such an overwhelming fragrance.

17
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,660
Sweet but not cloying.

18
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,680
Xi'er, you try some too.

19
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,720
You are kind, Boss.

20
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:24,480
But I dare not break the rules.

21
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,360
Try it.

22
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,320
Boss.

23
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,840
There's a distinguished guest outside.

24
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,760
They say they're from the palace.

25
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,610
People from the palace?

26
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,720
I, Xiao Jingyan,

27
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,480
risk my life to report to Your Majesty.

28
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,880
Prince Ling, Cui Tingru,

29
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,480
Minister of Works, Xie Wanshu,

30
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,840
and his son, Xie Yuheng,

31
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,200
colluded with Northern Di,

32
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,040
committed treason,

33
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,520
and massacred loyal subjects.

34
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,079
The evidence is conclusive.

35
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:50,960
Xiao Jingyan,

36
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:52,800
how dare you slander a prince in the Hall of Supreme Harmony

37
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:55,800
without any proof?

38
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,360
If I didn't have ironclad evidence,

39
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,090
why would I alarm Your Majesty?

40
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,440
Your Majesty.

41
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,920
The witness is waiting outside the hall.

42
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,920
Please examine this, Your Majesty.

43
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:15,680
Bring in the witness.

44
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,340
Greetings, Your Majesty.

45
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:25,770
Prince Ling.

46
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,360
Do you still recognize the word 'Treason'?

47
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,840
It is the merit branded

48
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,720
by your Black Armor Guard.

49
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,560
This flag

50
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:38,100
was taken back from the Beidi royal tent,

51
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:40,329
wrapping the Marquis's last remains.

52
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:42,100
Where is your conscience?

53
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,320
What you sent

54
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,290
were hollow swords and spears.

55
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,880
Three thousand brothers,

56
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,280
three thousand loyal souls,

57
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:50,320
were hacked to pieces by the Beidi people.

58
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,400
Their intestines

59
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:54,200
were hanging on the barbarians' saddles.

60
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,079
In the bloody battle at the border,

61
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:58,340
we protected the country with our lives,

62
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,920
but you supplied defective weapons,

63
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,780
causing our army's great defeat.

64
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,610
Three thousand heroic spirits

65
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,010
were buried in the sand.

66
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,320
May I ask Prince Ling,

67
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,570
these past three years,

68
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,960
at midnight,

69
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,120
have you ever heard

70
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:15,580
the crying of my three thousand brothers demanding your life?

71
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,040
When my father's head

72
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,160
was made into a wine vessel,

73
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,580
where were you?

74
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,960
You were in the dark,

75
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:34,560
forging swords and arrows for the Beidi.

76
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,600
Your Majesty.

77
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:41,780
This letter

78
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:46,120
is the ironclad proof of Prince Ling's collusion

79
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,340
with the Right Wise King of Beidi.

80
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:54,360
I beg Your Majesty to seek justice for my father

81
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:58,810
and the three thousand Zhenbei Army soldiers who died unjustly

82
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,040
for the country.

83
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:28,340
I pay my respects to the Empress Dowager.

84
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,920
Yan Qingshu,

85
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,880
it's been a long time.

86
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,159
I am humbled.

87
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,250
May I ask why you summoned me

88
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,320
and what decree you have?

89
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,400
Just a casual chat.

90
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,120
Offer her a seat.

91
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,320
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

92
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,480
I have heard...

93
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:51,560
The Duke possesses a record of hundred officials.

94
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:54,080
Have you ever heard of it?

95
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:56,290
To Empress Dowager,

96
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:59,000
I have never heard of it.

97
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,960
The record of hundred officials belongs to the royal family.

98
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,160
Three years ago,

99
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:07,080
the late emperor secretly entrusted it to the Duke for safekeeping.

100
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:09,120
Now the new emperor is enthroned,

101
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,800
and the court situation is newly settled.

102
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:13,260
It is time to return it to its rightful owner.

103
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,320
I am ignorant.

104
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,320
Since it belongs to the royal family,

105
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,980
why did the late emperor entrust it to my father?

106
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,320
The Empress Dowager is asking you a question.

107
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,780
How dare you question her?

108
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,640
I misspoke.

109
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:29,240
But my father has been missing for three years,

110
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,300
with no news at all.

111
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,409
I will return it when he comes back.

112
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,000
Very well.

113
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,520
I have one more thing

114
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:40,720
that I hope Miss Yan can part with.

115
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,720
You are too polite, Empress Dowager.

116
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:45,640
I would not dare refuse to give you anything I possess.

117
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:48,800
The Heishui Valley iron mine map.

118
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:53,000
Please understand, Empress Dowager.

119
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,760
I know nothing of this item.

120
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,730
Hand over what the Empress Dowager wants,

121
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,760
and you may still leave in one piece.

122
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,280
If you disobey again,

123
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:07,960
there will no longer be the legitimate eldest daughter of the Duke in this world,

124
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,320
Yan Qingshu.

125
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:19,960
Qingshu.

126
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:23,360
Hurry and hand over the records and mine map to the Empress Dowager.

127
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,690
Do you really want to get yourself killed?

128
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,520
Hand over the things,

129
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:33,040
and I can still beg the Empress Dowager to spare your life.

130
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,080
At this moment,

131
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,440
other than me,

132
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,440
who else can protect you?

133
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,980
Are you counting on Xiao Jingyan?

134
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,280
Your Majesty.

135
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,220
I have important matters.

136
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,480
I shall take my leave.

137
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,330
I'll leave your head

138
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,400
on your neck for now.

139
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,560
Next time,

140
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,040
I will take your life.

141
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,520
Prince Xiao

142
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,159
is truly a young hero.

143
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:42,679
Truly, like father, like son.

144
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,860
Let's see who dares touch her.

145
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,130
I will tear him to pieces

146
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,780
and scatter his ashes.

147
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:52,800
Your Majesty.

148
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,400
Your Majesty.

149
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,200
Your Majesty.

150
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,080
I am tired.

151
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,520
You may all leave.

152
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,040
I'm fine.

153
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,130
Are you all deaf?

154
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:15,160
Her Majesty is unwell.

155
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:17,320
Leave Zichen Palace at once.

156
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:20,530
Let's go.

157
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,480
Lord Xie,

158
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,560
you messed up this act

159
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,960
again.

160
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:37,130
What exactly is this Record of Officials?

161
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,200
You are indeed hiding something from me.

162
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:41,260
We'll talk after we leave the palace.

163
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,810
Prince Xiao,

164
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,160
today at the Hall of Supreme Harmony,

165
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,880
you drew your sword and alarmed His Majesty.

166
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,600
and trespassed in Zichen Palace again.

167
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,640
I will obey the decree.

168
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:59,500
You will be escorted to the Ministry of Justice prison to await trial.

169
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,720
Okay.

170
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,530
I'll go with you.

171
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:03,760
However,

172
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,320
I did this alone,

173
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,720
and it has nothing to do with anyone else.

174
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,780
Commander Qin, please let them pass.

175
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,400
Men,

176
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:14,380
escort the Duke's daughter out of the palace immediately.

177
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,960
Lord Xiao, excuse me.

178
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,620
I can't just leave him behind.

179
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,720
The Ministry of Justice prison is heavily guarded.

180
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,600
We can't force our way in.

181
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,920
I am under orders from the Heir

182
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,600
to escort Eldest Miss Yan home safely

183
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,400
without fail.

184
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,320
Home?

185
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:03,060
Where do I have a home anymore?

186
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:07,100
Escort Eldest Miss Yan back to Zhuque Tower.

187
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,800
I am going to save him.

188
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,120
Are you coming or not?

189
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,480
Disobeying military orders is punishable by death.

190
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,200
I won't go.

191
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:17,640
The Prince

192
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,440
might die.

193
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,200
Then what are we waiting for?

194
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,780
Knowing you like wine,

195
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,420
I prepared this fine wine.

196
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:48,120
You should savor it.

197
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:50,520
Such good wine,

198
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,650
you'd better save it for yourself.

199
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,280
On the way to the underworld,

200
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:20,200
Mengpo soup will accompany you.

201
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:20,840
Stop.

202
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,040
Qingshu.

203
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:32,760
Qingshu.

204
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:39,160
Xie Yuheng, how dare you poison him?

205
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,560
Give me the antidote.

206
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,720
If you want the antidote,

207
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:54,560
trade it for the Baiguan Xingshu and the Heishui Valley iron mine map.

208
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:55,240
Qingshu,

209
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,370
don't listen to him.

210
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,460
I don't have those things.

211
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,120
Yan Mingli said

212
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,760
you have the Heishui Valley iron mine map on you.

213
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,320
What if I say I don't?

214
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:12,160
Would you dare to poison the heir in this prison?

215
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,760
Why wouldn't I dare?

216
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:20,410
He destroyed the Xie family and stole my love.

217
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,000
He deserves to die.

218
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,290
Stole your love?

219
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,500
You are not worthy.

220
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,000
Qingshu.

221
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:36,680
I changed my mind.

222
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:41,440
You drink this poison,

223
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:44,010
and I'll give him the antidote.

224
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:44,850
How about it?

225
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,960
A life for a life.

226
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,080
You die,

227
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,200
he lives.

228
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:54,600
A life for a life.

229
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:55,520
You die,

230
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:57,520
and he lives.

231
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:07,840
Xie Yuheng.

232
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,320
Remember what you said,

233
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,520
a life for a life.

234
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:23,040
Qingshu.

235
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,250
If you dare break your oath,

236
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:40,480
my soul will fall into the infinite hell

237
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,600
and turn into an Asura.

238
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,160
For all eternity,

239
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,040
I will seek your life.

240
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:56,040
Qingshu.

241
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,200
Cuimei.

242
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:25,640
Yong.

243
00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:27,290
Huachao.

244
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:28,330
Weikun Huachao.

245
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:30,880
Long Cong Biao Hao.

246
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:35,060
Shuang Bin.

247
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:37,000
Ningzheng.

248
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:40,280
Hao Chun Kang Shuai Hua.

249
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:44,280
Wei Chao.

250
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:44,810
Weichao.

251
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,760
Qiang Yuan Liang Bo.

252
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:03,240
Xi.

253
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:04,520
Xi.

254
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:05,200
Xi.

255
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,360
Taoqiang.

256
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,440
Hui Yue Yun Qing.

257
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,640
Yiyi.

258
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:15,970
Yi Yi.

259
00:16:22,680 --> 00:16:23,280
Sisi.
